><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1136/pmj.76.898.457">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10908370/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=A+clinicopathological+classification+of+granulomatous+disorders&amp;author=DG+James&amp;publication_year=2000&amp;journal=Postgrad+Med+J&amp;pages=457-465&amp;doi=10.1136%2Fpmj.76.898.457&amp;pmid=10908370">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Williams GT, Williams WJ. Granulomatous inflammation: a review. <em>J Clin Pathol</em> 1983;36(7):723–733.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1136/jcp.36.7.723">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/6345591/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Granulomatous+inflammation%3A+a+review&amp;author=GT+Williams&amp;author=WJ+Williams&amp;publication_year=1983&amp;journal=J+Clin+Pathol&amp;pages=723-733&amp;doi=10.1136%2Fjcp.36.7.723&amp;pmid=6345591">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Gottschlich S, Ambrosch P, Kramkowski D, et al. Head and neck manifestations of Wegener’s granulomatosis. <em>Rhinology</em> 2006;44(4):227–233.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17216737/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Head+and+neck+manifestations+of+Wegener%E2%80%99s+granulomatosis&amp;author=S+Gottschlich&amp;au